{"id":"5fd20ff893a8961fc660a954","typeName":"Ammo","category":"ammo","parentTypeChain":["Ammo","StackableItem","Item"],"handbook":{"categoryId":"5b47574386f77428ca22b33b","price":870},"common":{"name":{"zh":".300 AAC 黑弹 AP","en":".300 Blackout AP"},"shortName":{"zh":"AP","en":"AP"},"description":{"zh":".300 BLK (7.62x35毫米) 穿甲弹配有重 8.4 克的 7.62x51 毫米 M80A1 同款穿甲弹头，采用黄铜衬套配钢制弹芯结构，外覆铜质半被甲。尽管 M80A1 作为一款全威力弹药的穿透性能十分突出，但以中间威力步枪弹的装药水平发射意味着其穿透能力和弹道性能会不可避免地受到影响。尽管如此，走低速重弹路线的 .300 BLK AP 仍能有效穿透中低等级的护甲，其停止作用也相当突出。.300 BLK 弹药可装填进 STANAG 规格的 5.56x45 毫米弹匣，但两款子弹并不能通用。","en":"A .300 Blackout (7.62x35mm) AP cartridge loaded with an 8.4 gram armor-piercing bullet from a 7.62x51mm NATO M80A1 cartridge, composed of a steel penetrator tip over a copper alloy core with a copper semi-jacket in a brass case. Despite the bullet's own characteristics when used in a full-power cartridge, these are affected when transferred to an intermediate cartridge, however, the bullet continues to have capabilities to pierce basic and intermediate body ballistic protections, in addition to being able to cause substantial adverse effects on the target after impact. Its design also allows it to be used in STANAG 5.56x45mm NATO magazines without any issues."},"weight":0.014,"width":1,"height":1,"rarity":"Superrare","backgroundColor":"yellow"},"properties":{"_raw":{"AmmoLifeTimeSec":5,"AmmoTooltipClass":"ArmorPiercing","AnimationVariantsNumber":0,"ArmorDamage":65,"ArmorDistanceDistanceDamage":{"x":0,"y":0,"z":0},"BackgroundColor":"yellow","BallisticCoeficient":0.334,"Blindness":{"x":0,"y":0,"z":0},"BulletDiameterMilimeters":7.8,"BulletMassGram":9.3,"Caliber":"Caliber762x35","CanRequireOnRagfair":false,"CanSellOnRagfair":false,"ConflictingItems":[],"Contusion":{"x":0,"y":0,"z":0},"Damage":51,"Description":"patron_762x35_blackout","Deterioration":1,"DiscardLimit":-1,"DiscardingBlock":false,"DropSoundType":"None","DurabilityBurnModificator":1.5,"ExamineExperience":10,"ExamineTime":1,"ExaminedByDefault":true,"Explosi